{"TopicId":79768,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Post-apocalyptic FPS games?","CreatedByName":"Wampa842","CreatedById":85841,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-27T20:48:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Wampa842","CreatedById":85841,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-27T20:48:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAfter playing the Fallout, Metro and STALKER games, I\u0027m really into this post-apocalyptic theme. Can anyone suggest a good post-apocalyptic story-based FPS game?\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-07-27T20:52:40Z\u0022 title=\u002207/27/2014 08:52  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 27, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Wampa842\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JokingHinge","CreatedById":109457,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-27T20:48:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDayZ standalone.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"7499275","CreatedById":70640,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-27T23:10:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENot a first person SHOOTER but I did see Scott Manley do a game called. \u0022the Long Dark\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZPLg966fpyE?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E \u003Cp\u003ELooks promising to say the least.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SelectHalfling0","CreatedById":105051,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-27T23:29:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMinecraft \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tery215","CreatedById":89094,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-27T23:38:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SelectHalfling0\u0022 data-cite=\u0022SelectHalfling0\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EMinecraft \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMinecraft isn\u0027t post-apocalyptic or a shooter. Nor is it story-based.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex","CreatedById":75164,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-27T23:47:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhile it may not be story-based, I would suggest Rust. It\u0027s sort of like Fallout without the story, and you make it up as you go along. It becomes really interesting when you have to be in close contact with other humans rather than NPCs for a change!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dbmorpher","CreatedById":77927,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-28T14:53:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAdventure Time Battle Party!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kryten","CreatedById":348,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-28T19:47:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EEarth: Year 2066.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dispatcher","CreatedById":78707,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-29T01:03:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhile Half Life might not qualify, all of Half Life 2 is in a post-invasion setting.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/ID1dWN3n7q4?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe game is available on Steam, for example.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rainbowtrout","CreatedById":60253,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-07-29T06:33:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIf you\u0027re into Apocalypse Survivals, there\u0027s Unturned. It\u0027s free on steam. The graphics aren\u0027t too good, but it is first-person, and you have lots of freedom.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}